history.proof: intros net H_refined. unfold candidates_vote_for_selves. intros h H_type. sauto lq: on depth: 3.

tactic: destruct (nwState net h) as [d |] eqn:H_nwState; simpl; try auto.
exceptions.exn: Expects a disjunctive pattern with 1 branch or a conjunctive pattern made of 2 patterns.

original: intros net H_refined. unfold candidates_vote_for_selves. intros h H_type. destruct (nwState net h) as [d |] eqn:H_nwState; simpl; try auto. apply cvfsi. apply H_type.
